thread.title: Cait
thread.title_full: PACK & SEND Australia reviewed by Cait

author: Cait
title: Cait
text:
Great customer service - very friendly, easy to contact, very helpful.
Quick delivery - despite national flooding my delivery still arrived by the ETA.
Safe delivery - box arrived in good condition (only one small tear in the box that didn't damage the insides), was well looked after until I was able to collect it.
Well priced - very reasonably price compared to other companies, good insurance policy
I would definitely use this service again and recommend it to others.
